{"_id":"05534496-e6aa-465b-8b5b-3a5efd9e8c9b","type":"Item","name":"Shadow 5: Shadowstalk","system":{"skill":"Shadow","name":"Shadowstalk","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"medium","defense":"intuition","Target":"Single/Area","range":"Short","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"3","description":"You may cast this spell on either a creature or an Obscured area. You become a part of the shadow, and are unseen but still aware of your surroundings. You gain an Epic Boon on all checks made to remain unseen and unnoticed. You are immune to all forms of damage except for Intuition and Intelligence damage, but cannot take actions. You can, however, end the spell at any time. If cast on a creature, you meld with their shadow, following it wherever it goes. Perfect darkness or full daylight end the effect immediately.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"0c0d9689-89d1-4b00-a137-91ed67afe96e","type":"Item","name":"Shadow 3: Umbra","system":{"skill":"Shadow","name":"Umbra","rank":"3","type":"technique","speed":"medium","defense":"","Target":"Area","range":"Short","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"2","description":"You create a cloud of darkness covering a Close range from the point you target. The area becomes Obscured and it becomes impossible to see into or out of it.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
