{"_id":"43dd0433-5142-4758-b88a-9198a1192f8f","type":"Item","name":"Shadow 5: Death's Embrace","system":{"skill":"Shadow","name":"Death's Embrace","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"medium","defense":"intuition","Target":"Multiple","range":"Short","Duration":"","cost":"3","description":"Targets each take Heavy Intuition damage. If they have the Dazed, Weakened, Slowed, Bleeding, Burning, Freezing, Charged, or Corroding condition they also immediately take an additional Wound.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"46e7aa07-d924-42bd-a55a-c6ba099cc35f","type":"Item","name":"Shadow 1: Sombre Cloak","system":{"skill":"Shadow","name":"Sombre Cloak","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"Self","range":"","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"1","description":"While maintaining this spell, you may use your Shadow skill in the place of your Stealth skill so long as you are not in areas of bright light.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"80be8362-1fdb-4357-9c1e-097dc7daf9ee","type":"Item","name":"Shadow 3: Nightmare","system":{"skill":"Shadow","name":"Nightmare","rank":"3","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"intuition","Target":"Single","range":"Adjacent","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"2","description":"You may only cast this spell on a sleeping target. You are able to control the target's dreams at will for as long as you maintain the spell. The target can be awoken through normal means, but does not wake due to the dreams themselves. If you have a sample of the creature's blood, a lock of their hair, or similar object, you may cast this spell from any range without seeing the target.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"933d255b-00ba-491e-903e-adecfc2fb37e","type":"Item","name":"Shadow 5: Hungering Darkness","system":{"skill":"Shadow","name":"Hungering Darkness","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"medium","defense":"intuition","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"3","description":"You call forth a floating sphere of all-consuming darkness. The sphere's area is shrouded in darkness and is obscured. At the end of each of your turns you must make a Shadow check against all creatures in its area, dealing Standard Intuition damage. Each round at the beginning of your turn it moves a Close distance toward the nearest living creature if no living creature is in its area. When you attempt to end this spell you must make a level 5 Shadow check; on a failure you may not try again until your next turn. If you fall unconscious, the sphere persists for 5 rounds afterward.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"d9e5a9c4-cb72-497d-bdf5-3f7ec3073127","type":"Item","name":"Shadow 1: Call of the Void","system":{"skill":"Shadow","name":"Call of the Void","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"inutition","Target":"Single","range":"Short","Duration":"Next","cost":"1","description":"The void calls to your target, darkening all they see. You deal Light Mind damage to the target. If you would cause a Major Wound, you may instead create a cloud of darkness that fills the target's area and renders it Obscured.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"ebc943c7-fa39-432d-bc30-692a586f7201","type":"Item","name":"Shadow 1: Sliver of Darkness","system":{"skill":"Shadow","name":"Sliver of Darkness","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"fast","defense":"intuition","Target":"Single","range":"Short","Duration":"","cost":"1","description":"This spell does Light Intuition damage to the target. If the target is unaware of your presence, it deals Heavy Intuition damage instead and grants Dazed. If you have entered your target's shadow using Shadowstalk, this can be cast while in that state but ends the spell.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
